OL,3,CWhy do voters give no credit to Sunak
OL,4,Cfor cutting taxes?
OL,6,FThis is not propaganda. It is endorsed
OL,7,Fby the Institute of Fiscal Studies
OL,8,F(IFS), which recently wrote that these
OL,9,Ftax gains would persist even after
OL,10,Fyears of the Tory government moving
OL,11,Fmillions of people into high tax
OL,12,Fbrackets by freezing thresholds.
OL,14,F"By 2027-28, after another three years
OL,15,Fof real-terms cuts to tax thresholds,
OL,16,Fthe net effect of income tax and NICs
OL,17,Fchanges since 2021 for the average
OL,18,Ffull-time earner will be a tax cut of
OL,19,F#140 per year," the Institute said.
