OL,3,CWhy do voters give no credit to Sunak
OL,4,Cfor cutting taxes?
OL,6,FFinally, as far as living standards
OL,7,Fare concerned, there has been a much
OL,8,Fbigger story than tax over the past 14
OL,9,Fyears since the Conservatives have
OL,10,Fbeen in government, namely that living
OL,11,Fstandards have flat-lined because of a
OL,12,Fcollapse in the growth of productivity
OL,13,F(our output per hour worked) and in
OL,14,Fearnings growth.
